+The `foundations` lane owns the **frontier-level** assessment view ‚Äî the curated artifact that tells the Raspberry control plane and human contributors the honest status of every bootstrap lane. It does not own the repair work for individual lanes; that belongs to the implementation lanes or restart lanes for each affected surface.
